                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17861213-44-off228 t17861213-44-cd229"></join> last, one iron mall, value 12 d. one hand-saw, value 15 d. one iron chissel, value 9 d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17861213-44-victim394" type="victimName">
